Terms & conditions are a legal agreement that outlines the rules for using a service, product, or website. 
Also known as terms of service / terms of use, these documents form a contract between a service provider and its user, requiring users to agree to specific guidelines before they can access the service. 
The primary purpose is to limit the provider's liability and protect their business by setting clear expectations. 
The documentalso outlines how the users' data will be used and handled by the service provider.
